---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Meet Kelly - Heartwood Wellbeing">
  <Navigation />

  <!-- Meet Kelly -->
  <section class="py-32">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif font-semibold text-warm-brown mb-12 text-center">Meet Kelly</h1>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="text-lg text-text-medium leading-relaxed">
          <img src="/assets/images/Meet Kelly .jpg" alt="Kelly - Heartwood Wellbeing Holistic Therapist" class="float-left mr-6 mb-4 w-64 h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-medium">
          
          <p class="mb-4">Hello, my name is Kelly, and I'm a Bespoke Senior Companion. I provide comforting holistic care tailored to each individual's needs – including massage, aromatherapy, sound therapy and of course meaningful conversation. My goal is to support well-being through connection, comfort and compassion.</p>
          
          <p class="mb-4">I am a trained Holistic Therapist with 26 years of experience working 1-1 with clients. Offering warmth and empathy, I bring together therapeutic skills and natural kindness to support seniors in feeling grounded, calm and heard.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-text-medium leading-relaxed">I have been working in the care home environment for the past year and have references to provide from Carers, Residents and Care home managers. I pride myself in the regular positive feedback I receive daily.</p>
        
        <blockquote class="bg-natural-beige p-8 rounded-2xl relative text-text-dark italic text-xl leading-relaxed clear-left">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 text-6xl text-dusty-rose">"</div>
          We didn't realise how much Mum needed this until we saw her smile after Kelly's visit. It's not just care. It's kindness, dignity and soul.
          <cite class="block text-right mt-4 font-semibold text-warm-brown not-italic">– Client's daughter</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }
</style> 